# docs-site

**Stack:** Next.js 16, React 19, Tailwind 4, Markdoc, motion (Framer Motion)

## Structure

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/app/` | Pages, layout, providers |
| `src/components/` | React components (Hero, Layout, Search) |
| `src/components/ui/` | shadcn-style UI primitives (terminal, blur-fade, border-beam) |
| `src/app/docs/` | Markdoc pages (`page.md`) |
| `src/lib/` | Utils, navigation |
| `src/markdoc/` | Markdoc nodes, config |

## Commands

```bash
cd docs-site && pnpm dev    # dev server
pnpm build && pnpm start    # prod
```

## Conventions

- Use `@/components/...` and `@/lib/...` aliases
- UI components in `src/components/ui/` use `cn()` for class merging
- Hero/landing lives in `src/components/Hero.tsx`
